 style=\"width:200px;text-align: right;white-space:nowrap;\"> <span>折扣率：87.00%</span> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div> </div> <h4><strong>四、主要标的信息</strong></h4> <div class=\"noticeBidResult-noticeBidResult _notice_content_noticeBidResult-noticeBidResult supplierDetail dynamic-form-editor\"> <div> <p class=\"u-content\">合同包1(阳江市中医医院机配型中药配方颗粒供应服务项目):</p> <div> <div> <p>服务类（广西仙茱制药有限公司）</p> <table width=\"100%\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\"> <thead> <tr style=\"height:36.4pt\"> <th style=\"width:80px;\">品目号</th> <th style=\"width:12%;\">品目名称</th> <th style=\"width:12%;\">采购标的</th> <th style=\"width:18%;\">服务范围</th> <th style=\"width:12%;\">服务要求</th> <th style=\"width:12%;\">服务时间</th> <th style=\"width:12%;\">服务标准</th> <!-- <th style=\"width:120px;text-align: right;word-break: normal;\">金额(元)</th> --> </tr> </thead> <tbody> <tr> <td>1-1</td> <td>医药和医疗器材批发服务</td> <td>阳江市中医医院机配型中药配方颗粒供应服务项目</td> <td>采购人指定地点</td> <td>机配型中药配方颗粒供应服务</td> <td>自合同签订生效之日起3年或实际采购金额达到采购预算金额，以两者先达到的为准。合同执行期间如遇国家或上级部门重大政策调整（如政府组织进行统一集中招标采购等），采购人和中标人均应遵守国家或上级部门的规定，双方视情况协商签订补充协议或无条件终止合同并执行相关政策文件，双方均不负赔偿责任。</td> <td>符合本项目招标文件要求</td> <!-- <td class=\"alignright\" th:text=\"${#numbers.formatDecimal(detail.totalPrice,1,'COMMA',4,'POINT')}\"></td> --> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div> </div> </div> </div> <h4><strong>五、评审专家（单一来源采购人员）名单：</strong></h4> <div class=\"noticeBidResult-noticeBidResult _notice_content_noticeBidResult-noticeBidResult expert\"> <p class=\"u-content\"><span><span>付启建</span><span>、</span></span><span><span>李小桂</span><span>、</span></span><span><span>费奕安</span><span>、</span></span><span><span>黄绍初</span><span>、</span></span><span><span>肖龙</span><span>、</span></span><span><span>李春莲</span><span>、</span></span><span><span>廖国东</span></span></p> </div> <h4><strong>六、代理服务收费标准及金额：</strong></h4> <div class=\"agentCharge-agentCharge _notice_content_agentCharge-agentCharge dynamic-form-editor\"> <table width=\"100%\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\"> <thead> <tr> <th colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:50%; height:36.4pt;\">代理服务收费标准</th> <th colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:50%; text-align: left;\"> <div style=\"float:none;\"> <p class=\"u-content\" style=\"text-indent: 0;\">以预算金额作为收费的计算依据，参照国家计委[计价格[2002]1980号]文及国家发改委[2011]534号文服务类招标代理服务收费标准差额定率累进法计算收取。</p> </div> </th> </tr> </thead> <tbody> <tr style=\"height:36.4pt;\"> <th>合同包号</th> <th>合同包名称</th> <th>代理服务费金额（万元）</th> <th>收取对象</th> </tr> <tr> <td style=\"width:15%;\">1</td> <td style=\"width:35%;text-align: left;\">阳江市中医医院机配型中药配方颗粒供应服务项目</td> <td class=\"alignright\" style=\"width:25%; text-align: right;white-space:nowrap;\">11.939273</td> <td style=\"width:30%;\">中标（成交）供应商</td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div> <h4><strong>七、公告期限</strong></h4> <p>自本公告发布之日起<span class=\"u-content noticeTerm-noticeTerm _notice_content_noticeTerm-noticeTerm dynamic-form-editor\" id=\"_notice_content_noticeTerm-noticeTerm\">1</span>个工作日。</p> <h4><strong>八、其他补充事宜</strong></h4> <p></p><div id=\"noticeResultDiv\"> <style type=\"text/css\">#noticeResultDiv { line-height:2.5; font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;font-family: '宋体';} #noticeResultDiv h1, #noticeResultDiv h2, #noticeResultDiv h3, #noticeResultDiv h4, #noticeResultDiv h5, #noticeResultDiv h6{ line-height: 2; } #noticeResultDiv p, #noticeResultDiv strong, #noticeResultDiv pre{ line-height: 2.5; } #noticeResultDiv *{padding:0; margin:0;} #noticeResultDiv .focuscontent{ color:#337ab7;} #noticeResultDiv strong{ font-weight: bold;} #noticeResultDiv h2{font-size: 24px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;} #noticeResultDiv h3{font-size: 18px;font-weight: normal;} #noticeResultDiv h4{font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;} #noticeResultDiv h5{text-indent: 32px;font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;} #noticeResultDiv h6{font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;} #noticeResultDiv em{ font-weight: normal;font-style: italic;} #noticeResultDiv pre{font-size: 16px;background: none;border: none;line-height: 2.5;} #noticeResultDiv p{ text-indent: 32px; font-size: 16px;} #noticeResultDiv bs{ text-inden